      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable choice for someone looking for a solid daily driver. Mechanically, the engine and transmission are functioning well, and it has been regularly serviced to ensure reliability on the road. However, the exterior shows visible signs of age, including some minor scratches and paint fading in a few spots. The interior is clean but has some wear on the upholstery and dashboard that reflects its years of use. It is a practical, honest car that gets the job done without any major mechanical surprises.",
