    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for all my daily trips. It drives like a dream and still looks great parked in the driveway! If you're looking for a reliable, well-cared-for car that's ready to hit the road today, this is the one. I'd love for it to go to a great new home, so come check it out and see for yourself!",
      "price": 31500.0,
