      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This driver-spec example is equipped with a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term chassis rigidity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced\u2014a vital preventative measure for this platform. Performance remains peak with a recently serviced VANOS system and a fresh valve shim adjustment, ensuring the individual throttle bodies deliver immediate, linear throttle response. The suspension maintains its factory-intended kinematics, providing communicative feedback through the apex. While the aesthetic reflects honest road use, the drivetrain remains tight and the power delivery is visceral up to the 8,000 RPM redline.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Mechanically sound. Clean title. Regular service history. Interior well-kept.",
